Interface UserEquipmentDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JPAUserEquipmentDAO

    public interface UserEquipmentDAO
    User Equipment Data Access Object

    User Equipment data access object contains abstract methods to implement CRUD operations for User Equipment object.

    Author:
    John O Keeffe, Eoin Kernan, James Mc Ternan
